  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/ad2a6fe9a9963ac7e4f2e741fcec90a7.poster.avif?t=1718832707\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/ad2a6fe9a9963ac7e4f2e741fcec90a7.webm?t=1718832707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/ad2a6fe9a9963ac7e4f2e741fcec90a7.mp4?t=1718832707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Feathered Serpent is a <strong>roguelike</strong> action platformer that pairs <strong>fast-paced combat</strong> with <strong>randomly generated</strong> levels, enemies, and items!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WAR AGAINST THE DINOSAURS</h2>Battle against a race of dinosaur-people known as the <strong>Saurians</strong>. Exact revenge upon them for sacrificing your people to Quetzalcoatl, The Feathered Serpent. Just beware the raptors...<strong> clever girls.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/cad474e268d8ecd5a431eb37ef1c45bd.avif?t=1718832707\" width=630 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLIMITED ITEM SYNERGIES</h2>Well, to be more precise, there are <strong>exactly</strong> 1,087,562,120,541,668,200,000,000,000,000 potential item combinations to enjoy. As you progress through this lost world, random item drops will change the way your character <strong>moves and attacks.</strong> Experiment to find the best<strong> item combinations </strong>in each attempt to slay The Feathered Serpent. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/1b957179d25dc18829a10e91d282faf6.apng?t=1718832707\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/1b957179d25dc18829a10e91d282faf6.poster.avif?t=1718832707\" class=\"bb_img\" width=631 height=209 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME FRIENDS WITH CATS, BIRDS, AND SHARKS</h2>Experience <strong>hundreds</strong> of unique story events that are interconnected between the many NPC's you will run into during your adventures. Anyone who isn't a dinosaur is a welcome ally... except for that rogue dinosaur shopkeeper<strong> Brazak,</strong> I guess he seems pretty cool.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENDLESS REPLAYABILITY</h2>Each new attempt will have you encountering <strong>new </strong>enemies, dinosaurs, and bosses. Watch how bosses progressively become harder each time you defeat them. Experience how <strong>the game grows with you</strong> and changes as a result of your actions.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/ad2a6fe9a9963ac7e4f2e741fcec90a7.poster.avif?t=1718832707\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/ad2a6fe9a9963ac7e4f2e741fcec90a7.webm?t=1718832707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/ad2a6fe9a9963ac7e4f2e741fcec90a7.mp4?t=1718832707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Feathered Serpent is a <strong>roguelike</strong> action platformer that pairs <strong>fast-paced combat</strong> with <strong>randomly generated</strong> levels, enemies, and items!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WAR AGAINST THE DINOSAURS</h2>Battle against a race of dinosaur-people known as the <strong>Saurians</strong>. Exact revenge upon them for sacrificing your people to Quetzalcoatl, The Feathered Serpent. Just beware the raptors...<strong> clever girls.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/cad474e268d8ecd5a431eb37ef1c45bd.avif?t=1718832707\" width=630 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLIMITED ITEM SYNERGIES</h2>Well, to be more precise, there are <strong>exactly</strong> 1,087,562,120,541,668,200,000,000,000,000 potential item combinations to enjoy. As you progress through this lost world, random item drops will change the way your character <strong>moves and attacks.</strong> Experiment to find the best<strong> item combinations </strong>in each attempt to slay The Feathered Serpent. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/1b957179d25dc18829a10e91d282faf6.apng?t=1718832707\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832240/extras/1b957179d25dc18829a10e91d282faf6.poster.avif?t=1718832707\" class=\"bb_img\" width=631 height=209 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME FRIENDS WITH CATS, BIRDS, AND SHARKS</h2>Experience <strong>hundreds</strong> of unique story events that are interconnected between the many NPC's you will run into during your adventures. Anyone who isn't a dinosaur is a welcome ally... except for that rogue dinosaur shopkeeper<strong> Brazak,</strong> I guess he seems pretty cool.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENDLESS REPLAYABILITY</h2>Each new attempt will have you encountering <strong>new </strong>enemies, dinosaurs, and bosses. Watch how bosses progressively become harder each time you defeat them. Experience how <strong>the game grows with you</strong> and changes as a result of your actions.",
